'''克瓦納過程'''（{{lang-en|Kværner process}}），或稱為'''克瓦納碳黑和氫氣過程'''（{{lang-en|Kværner carbon black and hydrogen process}}；簡稱'''CB&H'''），是一種從[[碳氫化合物|碳氫化合物]]（如[[甲烷|甲烷]]、[[天然氣|天然氣]]或[[生物燃氣|生物燃氣]]等）生產[[碳黑|碳黑]]和[[氫氣|氫氣]]的過程，該過程無[[溫室氣體|溫室氣體]]產生。該過程係由[[挪威|挪威]]工程公司{{le|克瓦納|Kværner}}於1980年代研發，並於1999年首度進行商業化<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.interstatetraveler.us/Reference-Bibliography/Bellona-HydrogenReport.html|title = Bellona Report 6:02, "Hydrogen - Status and possibilities" Hydrogen technologies|publisher = Bellona Foundation|website = Interstate Traveler Company|accessdate = 13 March 2014|archive-date = 2016-06-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160603020122/http://www.interstatetraveler.us/Reference-Bibliography/Bellona-HydrogenReport.html}}</ref>。經改進的克瓦納過程可在低成本下增加[[甲烷|甲烷]][[熱裂解|熱解]]處理量。

該過程在1600°C的[[電漿|電漿]]燃燒爐中經[[吸熱反應|吸熱反應]]將碳氫化合物分解為碳和氫；碳粒和氫氣形成氣溶膠型態的混合物<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kuehl|first=Olaf|date=|year=2016|title=US 9,309,125 B2 - PROCESS AND SYSTEM FOR GENERATING SYNTHESIS GAS - Caphenia / CCP Technology Description [0048]|url=https://worldwide.espacenet.com/patent/search/family/048522145/publication/US9309125B2?q=pn%3DUS9309125B2|access-date=2019-11-28|website=worldwide.espacenet.com|publisher=European Patent Office EPO}}</ref>。
:<chem>C_\mathit{n}H_\mathit{m} -> {\mathit{n}C} + \frac{\mathit{m}}{2} H2</chem> 
相較於[[蒸汽重組|蒸汽重組]]和{{le|部分氧化|Partial oxidation}}等過程會產生副產物[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]，克瓦納過程沒有副產物。天然氣被有效率且完全地轉化為純碳和氫，過程中不釋放二氧化碳至大氣中。分離混合物後，碳粒可用做[[活性碳|活性碳]]、[[石墨|石墨]]、工業塵灰或特規碳材（如碳盤和碳錐）等。碳以黑色粉粒被收集，並可衍伸應用在[[橡膠|橡膠]]填料、油墨和油漆的顏料塵灰、或用作電氣組件的原料。氫氣則可提供[[化學程序|化工程序]]使用或者用於[[發電|發電]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kuehl|first=Olaf|date=|year=2019|title=US 10166521 B2 - Process and system for conversion of carbon dioxide to carbon monixide - Caphenia / CCP Technology - Description|url=https://worldwide.espacenet.com/patent/search/family/048522145/publication/US10166521B2?q=us10166521|access-date=2019-11-28|website=worldwide.espacenet.com|publisher=European Patent Office EPO}}</ref>。過程輸入的能量有48%用於生產氫氣，40%用於生產活性碳，而10%用於產生過熱蒸汽<ref>[https://www.hfpeurope.org/infotools/energyinfos__e/hydrogen/main03.html hfpeurope.org]{{dead link|date=March 2014}}</ref><!--Previously tagged as "secure page, not accesible"-->。基於{{le|電漿氣化|Plasma gasification}}的衍伸製程於2009年被提出；甲烷和天然氣在電漿轉化反應器中被轉化為氫氣、熱和碳<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://fuelcellsworks.com/news/2009/10/12/hydrogen-breakthrough-for-norwegian-company/|title = Hydrogen Breakthrough for Norwegian company|accessdate = 13 March 2014|date = 12 October 2009|website = FuelCellsWorks|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313194912/http://fuelcellsworks.com/news/2009/10/12/hydrogen-breakthrough-for-norwegian-company/|archive-date = 13 March 2014}}</ref>。

